assets.name: assets/3wuytTnJjQ7
assets.description:
Tomatoes, launched from outer space!
GMO free Tomato Raygun.
The Tomatron 82 uses type IV vortex crystals to duplicate the enclosed source mini tomato on the back and materialize a clone in the front crystal. The clone tomato is given a will in the process along with an antigravity capability. 
Once out the clone tomato is seeking for any hard surface to splash on. Use at your own risks. Vegan friendly.
